snippet.title: Mile High Pinball - N-Gage - Gameplay
snippet.description:
I was playing more of this and found it has a crossover with Pathway to Glory where you hit the tanks. Video in this tweet https://twitter.com/adeeelnv/status/1286807877898838018?s=19
The game is good, but it can be really difficult to get the ball to go where you want. I really like the concept of clearing objectives to continue upwards.
